---
By: Dalai Lama
Source:
  URL: https://twitter.com/DalaiLama/status/1005019375957471232
  Locus:
    Date: 8 Jun 2018
---
In today’s interconnected and globalized world, it’s now commonplace
for people of different world views, faiths and races to live side by
side. It’s a matter of great urgency, therefore, that we find ways to
cooperate with one another in a spirit of mutual acceptance and respect.
